title: Continuation of the Exercise of Certain Authorities Under the Trading With the Enemy Act
summary: The document is a presidential determination (No. 202511) issued on August 29, 2025, continuing the exercise of certain authorities under the Trading with the Enemy Act with respect to Cuba for one year, until September 14, 2026. This action is deemed necessary in the national interest of the United States and is implemented through the Cuban Assets Control Regulations (31 CFR Part 515). The Secretary of the Treasury is directed to publish this determination in the Federal Register.
